com.ibm.watson.dsm.platform

Class AbstractStorageQuery<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.watson.dsm.platform.AbstractStorageQuery<DESC,DATA>
  • Type Parameters:
    DESC -
    DATA -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDataQuery<DESC,DATA>, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractBeanQuery, NamedDataQuery

    public abstract class AbstractStorageQuery<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDataQuery<DESC,DATA>
    Implements methods defined in IDataQuery interface and allows selection of shared data from the platform's IDataStorage instance. Names of data items, as assigned within the IDataStorage, instanced may be used to specify the item(s). If names are provided, then only those shared data with one of the given names are considered by the query. Sub-classes must implement the isDataMatch(ISharedData) to possibly refine the query to specifics within the shared data, such as instance field values.
    Author:
    dawood
